About this property

Elegant Accommodations: Marasa Sarovar Premiere in Bodhgaya offers a 5-star experience with family rooms, air-conditioning, and private bathrooms. Each room includes a work desk, city view, and free WiFi. Exceptional Facilities: Guests enjoy a fitness center, year-round outdoor swimming pool, and a lush garden. Additional amenities include a coffee shop, child-friendly buffet, and free on-site private parking. Dining Experience: The family-friendly restaurant serves Indian cuisine with vegetarian and dairy-free options. Breakfast includes continental, American, and local specialties. Dining options include brunch, lunch, dinner, and high tea. Prime Location: Located 3.7 mi from Gaya International Airport, the hotel is near Mahabodhi Temple (1.9 mi) and Bodh Gaya Bus Station (1.9 mi). Other attractions include Thai Monastery (2.5 mi) and Great Buddha Statue (3.1 mi).
